sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae2a0d2c86711ce4734d05097a868f99ee2c1fcb","tid":959162,"uid":51612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"47760d94baf961da4695bf0952fe5e9c6a6b94a1","tid":959162,"uid":49626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T16:09:37.000Z","msg":"學左荷蘭咁大麻合法化 仲唔全港回歸大陸懷抱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T17:21:34.000Z","msg":"以香港人既質素，反對多過讚成五倍都有。"},{"pid":"56278450bc33e029683a760f0efa5174265ad24d","tid":959162,"uid":4964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3a1bd4fc05fa6181f2c43f736a25735216038207","tid":959162,"uid":59570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T11:21:47.000Z","msg":"大麻合法化基本就係世界趨勢<br />\n<br />\n香港呢d高壓奴隸制更加應該合法化<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T17:24:36.000Z","msg":"中國有種又唔同講法啦<br />\n話唔定好快特區政府同衛生署跑出嚟話大麻好處多<br />\n要合法化,係河套區整個大灣區一小時大麻生活圈"},{"pid":"2702137bd440f43545e732db1e696d7c2aa64ce8","tid":959162,"uid":98551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T17:24:41.000Z","msg":"強國係咪想學以前鴉片戰爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acc5639b1e194d99de48ccf15f01d750234df298","tid":959162,"uid":59570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56278450bc33e029683a760f0efa5174265ad24d","tid":959162,"uid":4964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3a1bd4fc05fa6181f2c43f736a25735216038207","tid":959162,"uid":59570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T11:21:47.000Z","msg":"大麻合法化基本就係世界趨勢<br />\n<br />\n香港呢d高壓奴隸制更加應該合法化<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T17:24:36.000Z","msg":"中國有種又唔同講法啦<br />\n話唔定好快特區政府同衛生署跑出嚟話大麻好處多<br />\n要合法化,係河套區整個大灣區一小時大麻生活圈"},"citedBy":0,